            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數下跌-174.98點至5661.3點，跌幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日11:22，恆生科技指數下跌174.98點（或3%），暫報5661.30點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+1.54%</li><li>近 1 月：+6.11%</li><li>近 3 月：+31.32%</li><li>近 6 月：+57.57%</li><li>今年以來：+30.62%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>汽車概念領跌-4.15%。其中    北京汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01958-HK</a>)            下跌        12.4%            ;        比亞迪股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01211-HK</a>)            下跌        7.31%            ;        吉利汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00175:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00175\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00175-HK</a>)            下跌        5.15%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>生物科技概念領跌-3.23%。其中    康方生物(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09926:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09926\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09926-HK</a>)            下跌        7.72%            ;        復宏漢霖(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02696:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https:/